WEBVTT

00:11.000 --> 00:18.500
Right now, I'm here at IBT Institute...

00:18.500 --> 00:23.000
and Sir Ali's student, Sufiyan...

00:23.000 --> 00:28.500
has done my haircut.

00:28.500 --> 00:36.000
He has given me a complete fade with a full hair cut...

00:36.000 --> 00:40.000
and MashaAllah...

00:40.000 --> 00:48.500
you can clearly see the sharpness and cleanliness.

00:48.500 --> 00:53.000
If you look closely...

00:53.000 --> 01:01.000
the level of perfection in his hands...

01:01.000 --> 01:09.000
to be honest, not many people can achieve this kind of perfection.

01:09.000 --> 01:18.000
So, a big thank you to Sir Ali...

01:18.000 --> 01:23.500
and especially to Sufiyan...

01:23.500 --> 01:27.000
for this amazing haircut.

01:27.000 --> 01:29.000
Thank you!